h1. About this Chapter

This section describes the process of creating a policy definition.  It includes an in-depth description of the Simple Text V1 lexicon and tools for
creating and testing policy definitions.

* [Simple Text Lexicon|./tools-simpleTextV1.html] Full syntax rules and description of the Simple Text Lexicon.
* [Policy Builder|./tools-policyBuilder.html] Simple text editor based tool for writing and testing policies written in the Simple Text Lexicon.
* [Examples|./tools-examplePolicies.html] Some example policies for common use cases.

